snippet.title: CYBERDRIFTER - Enter Cyberspace in Virtual Reality!
snippet.description:
Join the Cyberdrifter team and battle through Cyberspace destroying all rogue AI in a virtual mainframe!

Early access available:  Oculus Rift - HTC Vive - Mixed Reality

https://www.uzigames.co.uk/

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/607760/Cyberdrifter/
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1382713051820964/
WearVR: https://www.wearvr.com/apps/cyberdrifter
